title: 08/29: Sleepers/Breakouts/Busts 3.0; Emails and Regulators! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Starting with some important questions like players we're willing to reach for (2:15), players we pretty much never draft (5:10), when to draft Ezekiel Elliott (6:45) and our biggest preseason risers and fallers (10:00) ... News and notes (13:00), wrapping up our conversation about how to draft from each spot in the draft (17:00), then a fresh look at some sleepers (26:00), breakouts (33:40) and busts (40:40)! Disagreement on Darren Waller and Matt Ryan. How about Sammy Watkins, Mitchell Trubisky and Leonard Fournette? ... Regulators (51:00)! We're ruling on some questionable stuff going on in your leagues ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
